1. *Završili* smo prošlog meseca. (We finished last month.)
2. Oni su pre nekoliko dana *završili* svoj projekat. (They finished their project a few days ago.)
3. Doktor je *završio* pregled pre nekoliko sati. (The doctor finished the examination a few hours ago.)
4. Oni su *završili* svoj put pre tri nedelje. (They finished their journey three weeks ago.)
5. *Završio* sam knjigu pre nekoliko nedelja. (I finished the book a few weeks ago.)
6. Oni su *završili* svoju reč pre nekoliko minuta. (They finished their speech a few minutes ago.)